title: May 9th - Basic Bitch Quickie (BBQ) Weekly - Selling Sunset Season 5 Overview(Featuring Paul Imbro)
itunes:title: May 9th - Basic Bitch Quickie (BBQ) Weekly - Selling Sunset Season 5 Overview(Featuring Paul Imbro)
itunes:subtitle: Christine, Christine, Christine....did we miss anything?
description:
This week, while the Brain is still in the "motherland", the Basic continues to co-host BBQs with the best of the best! This week we have former guest Paul Imbro (Paul is a former morning show and reality TV producer turned real estate agent in good old Los Angeles) joining us to talk all things Selling Sunset. As season 5 comes to a close with the reunion having aired this week, Paul and Aleena sip on ALL the tea, from Chrishell Stause and Jason Oppenheimer's breakup, to how we feel about Selling Sunset's newcomer Chelsea Lanzkani, to how Maya is still the boring one (according to Paul) and even Chrishell's most recent relationship update.



Don't forget to follow us, review our podcast and subscribe on our socials!

  • Twitter: @BasicandBrain
  • Instagram: @TheBasicandTheBrain
  • TikTok: @thebasic_and_thebrain
  • Website: thebasicandthebrain.com

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
